<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Diagnoz bir topar alamatlar
arkaly edil&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in bedend&auml;ki
&auml;hli bozulmalar, &uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler,
&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;iklikler barada lukmana a&yacute;tmak
m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Genetiki synag&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- degi&#351;li genlerde
&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;iklik &yacute;ok bolsa, seliaki&yacute;a
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&#350;ol bir wagty&#328; &ouml;z&uuml;nde,
seliaki&yacute;ani&#328; genetiki bellikleri bolan adamlary&#328; 30% -i bu
keseli &ouml;sd&uuml;rme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>So&#328;ky &auml;hli
synaglar, gl&yacute;uten bedene girende &ouml;nd&uuml;ril&yacute;&auml;n
antikorlary &quot;tut&yacute;ar&quot;, &#351;onu&#328;&nbsp;<b>&uuml;&ccedil;in
adaty, gl&yacute;utsiz i&yacute;mitlenmeli&nbsp;</b>:&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dokuma transglutaminaza IgA antikorlary&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>endomizi&yacute;a gar&#351;y antikorlar&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;l&ccedil;elenen
parametrler k&ouml;plen&ccedil; &uuml;&yacute;tg&auml;p dur&yacute;arlar,
&#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in negatiw netijeleri alsa&#328;yz, synaglary
t&auml;zeden ge&ccedil;irmegi&#328; manysy bar.&nbsp;O&#328;yn netijeler
diagnozy tassyklamak &uuml;&ccedil;in be&yacute;leki synaglary&#328;
ge&ccedil;irilmegini talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Birn&auml;&ccedil;e &yacute;erden in&ccedil;e
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; (on iki barmakly i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;)&nbsp;<b>gyjyndyrmasyny&#328;
biopsi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;A&#351;gazany&#328; we on iki&nbsp;<b>barmakly&nbsp;</b>i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
endoskopiki barlagy bilen ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r (&nbsp;<b>EGD&nbsp;</b>).&nbsp;T&uuml;&yacute;k&uuml;lik
dokumasyny&#328; gurlu&#351;yny&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgemegi keseli takyk
anyklamaga m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute;da zy&yacute;an &ccedil;eken &yacute;ere barmazlyk
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;iligi bar, &#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in negatiw netije seliaki&yacute;ani&#328;
&yacute;oklugyna 100% ynam berme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;agalara simptomlara,
genetiki synaglary&#328; netijelerine we antikor synaglaryna esaslanyp
biopsi&yacute;a bolmazdan diagnoz go&yacute;up bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Diagnoz tassyklanan
