color:black'> &uuml;&ccedil;in gl&yacute;ukokortikoidler, belok-energi&yacute;a
&yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi bilen keseli&#328; agyr gidi&#351;inde bellenilip
bilner.&nbsp;</span></p>

